org.chocosolver.memory

Interface IStorage

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IOperationTrail, IStoredBoolTrail, IStoredDoubleTrail, IStoredIntTrail, IStoredLongTrail
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ChunckedBoolTrail, ChunckedDoubleTrail, ChunckedIntTrail, ChunckedLongTrail, ChunckedOperationTrail, ChunckedTrail, OperationTrail, StoredBoolTrail, StoredDoubleTrail, StoredDoubleVectorTrail, StoredIntTrail, StoredIntVectorTrail, StoredLongTrail

    public interface IStorage
    An interface for classes implementing trails of modifications to objects.

    Toutes les classes doivent implementer les fonctions de l'interface pour permettre a l'environnement de deleguer la gestion des mondes pour chaque type de donnee.
